Package org.sopra.api.model

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Controllable
    Controllable is an interface that allows to gain information about controllable graph elements.
    Edge<V>
    The egde of a graph.
    EnergyNode
    Nodes in a scenario graph.
    Graph<N,E extends Edge<N>>
    Class representing a directed capacitated graph.
    PlantLocation
    Plant location is data container that holds both an energy node and the playfield element with the same coordinates.
    Playfield
    The playfield represents the land where the scenario is located.
    PlayfieldElement
    One tile of the playfield.
    PowerLine
    The data type for the actual power lines in the scenario.
    TransformerStation
    Transformer stations are "empty" nodes.

    PowerLineType
    An enumeration to simplify the selection of the type of a power line.
